  "remarks": "Member of the Rajah Solaiman Movement (QDe.128). Fathers name is Feliciano Delos Reyes Sr. Mothers name is Aurea Semborio. In detention in the Philippines as of May 2011. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 13 May 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.; Listing: Resolution 1735 (2006) Listed on: 4 June. 2008 (amended 3 June 2009, 13 Dec. 201, 6 Dec 2019)",
